.SH DATA TYPES
.LP
.B
\fBdictionary() :: module().\fR

.br
.RS
.PP
The name of a generated dictionary module as generated by diameterc(1) or \fIdiameter_make:codec/2\fR. The interface provided by a dictionary module is an implementation detail that may change.


.RE
.B
\fBmessage() :: record() | maybe_improper_list().\fR

.br
.RS
.PP
The representation of a Diameter message as passed to \fIdiameter:call/4\fR or returned from a handle_request/3 callback.


.RE
.B
\fBpacket() :: #diameter_packet{}.\fR

.br
.RS
.PP
A container for incoming and outgoing Diameter messages.


.RE
.SH FUNCTIONS
.LP
.B
\fBdecode(Mod, Bin) -> Pkt\fR
\fB                when\fR
\fB                    Mod :: dictionary(),\fR
\fB                    Bin :: binary(),\fR
\fB                    Pkt :: packet().\fR

.br
.RS
.PP
Decode a Diameter message.


.RE
.B
\fBencode(Mod, Msg) -> Pkt\fR
\fB                when\fR
\fB                    Mod :: dictionary(),\fR
\fB                    Msg :: message() | packet(),\fR
\fB                    Pkt :: packet().\fR

.br
.RS
.PP
Encode a Diameter message.


.RE
